title: Revenue Ton-Miles Per Locomotive Assigned to Freight Service for United States
notes:
Data For January 1920 Were Not Available For Series 01250. Source: Computed By NBER By Dividing Seasonal Values Of Series 03003 Revenue Ton-Miles) By Seasonal Values Of Series 01250 (Total Locomotives Assigned To Freight Service).
